OL,3,CPC posed as paedophile hunter to
OL,4,Cblackmail suspect
OL,6,FA police officer tried to blackmail a
OL,7,Fsuspected sex offender by posing as a
OL,8,Fpaedophile hunter and threatening to
OL,9,Fpublicise his arrest.
OL,11,FPC Marie Thompson, 29, then tried to
OL,12,Fcover her tracks when the man refused
OL,13,Fto hand over #3,500 and instead called
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire Police.
OL,16,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,17,Fsaid Thompson arrested and interviewed
OL,18,Fthe man in October 2022 on suspicion
OL,19,Fof possessing indecent images, before
OL,20,Fhe was released under investigation.
