OL,6,FThree months later, the man received
OL,7,Fan email from a ProtonMail address
OL,8,Fdemanding #3,500 be paid into a bank
OL,9,Faccount, with an account number and
OL,10,Fsort code provided.
OL,12,FThe email, purporting to be from self-
OL,13,Fstyled paedophile hunters said the
OL,14,Fpayment would "ensure that information
OL,15,Fremains between you and us".
OL,17,FLater the same day, the man's partner
OL,18,Freceived a text message demanding a
OL,19,Freply by the end of the day.
