OL,3,CPC posed as paedophile hunter to
OL,4,Cblackmail suspect
OL,6,FThe man ignored the demand and
OL,7,Freported the correspondence to South
OL,8,FYorkshire Police.
OL,10,FHis complaint was forwarded to
OL,11,FThompson, who told the man she would
OL,12,Finvestigate.
OL,14,FInstead she closed the crime report,
OL,15,Ffalsely claiming he did not want to
OL,16,Fpursue a complaint, the CPS said.
OL,18,FThe investigation was closed, and
OL,19,FThompson lied again to the man six
OL,20,Fweeks later, claiming the email and
OL,21,Ftext message could not be traced.
