OL,4,Cblackmail suspect
OL,6,FThompson, who was suspended from South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police in March 2023 for
OL,8,Fother matters, was later found to have
OL,9,Fsent the text from PC Thompson's
OL,10,Fpersonal mobile phone.
OL,12,FExamination of her laptop also showed
OL,13,Fshe had also sent the email.
OL,15,FPc Thompson, who is still suspended
OL,16,Ffrom the force, pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fblackmail and perverting the course of
OL,18,Fjustice on Thursday at Leeds Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
