OL,6,FShe will be sentenced at the same
OL,7,Fcourt on 30 October.
OL,9,FThe prosecution followed an
OL,10,Finvestigation by South Yorkshire
OL,11,FPolice's professional standards
OL,12,Fdepartment.
OL,14,FMalcolm McHaffie, head of the CPS
OL,15,FSpecial Crime Division, said: "Pc
OL,16,FMarie Thompson tried to abuse her
OL,17,Fposition as the investigating police
OL,18,Fofficer in this case for financial
OL,19,Fgain.
